"intervals específics de Weblate. Configureu-lo "
"amb :setting:`OPENTELEMETRY_ENABLED`, :setting:`OPENTELEMETRY_EXPORTER_OTLP_ENDPOINT` "
"i :setting:`OPENTELEMETRY_TRACES_SAMPLE_RATE`."

