#: changes/v5.rst:173
msgid ""
":ref:`check-end-interrobang` now recognizes Arabic interrobang punctuation "
"such as ``؟!`` and ``!؟``."
msgstr ""
":ref:`check-end-interrobang` ara reconeix la puntuació interrobang àrab com "
