#: changes/v5.rst:177
msgid ""
"The ``project_scope`` class attribute on add-ons has been removed. Third-"
"party add-ons that used ``project_scope = True`` should override "
"``can_install()`` to return ``False`` when ``component`` is not ``None``."
msgstr ""
"S'ha eliminat l'atribut de classe ``project_scope`` dels complements. Els "
"complements de tercers que utilitzaven ``project_scope = True`` haurien "
"d'anul·lar ``can_install()`` per tornar ``False`` quan ``component`` no "
"sigui ``None``."

#: changes/v5.rst:178
msgid ""
"The ``daily()`` method signature on add-ons has changed. Add-ons that "
"previously overrode ``daily(component)`` to perform per-component work "
"should now override ``daily_component(component)`` instead. The base "
"``daily()`` method automatically iterates components and calls "
"``daily_component()`` for each. Add-ons that can be optimized to operate at "
"project scope should override ``daily(component, project)`` directly to "
"implement project-level logic."
msgstr ""
"La signatura del mètode ``daily()`` als complements ha canviat. Els "
"complements que anteriorment substituïen ``daily(component)`` per realitzar "
"treballs per component ara haurien de substituir "
"``daily_component(component)``. El mètode base ``daily()`` itera "
"automàticament components i crida ``daily_component()`` per a cadascun. Els "
"complements que es poden optimitzar per funcionar a l'abast del projecte "
"haurien d'anul·lar ``diari (component, projecte)`` directament per "
"implementar la lògica a nivell de projecte."

#: changes/v5.rst:179
msgid "Dropped support for MySQL and MariaDB as the database engine."
msgstr ""
"S'ha eliminat el suport per a MySQL i MariaDB com a motor de base de dades."

#: changes/v5.rst:180
