#: contributing/communication.rst:2
msgid "Weblate Contributor Communication Guidelines"
msgstr "Directrius de comunicació per a col·laboradors del weblate"

#: contributing/communication.rst:5
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "GitHub username"
msgid "GitHub Issues"
msgstr "Nom d’usuari al GitHub"

#: contributing/communication.rst:6
msgid ""
"`GitHub Issues <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/weblate/issues>`_ is where "
"bugs can be reported, and features can be requested. Issue submission form "
"provides templates for each to simplify issue creation, and review and "
"implementation process; it also guides to other places with information like "
"documentation, Discussions, HackerOne program, and Weblate Care."
msgstr ""
"`Problemes de GitHub <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/weblate/issues>`_ és on "
"es poden informar d'errors i es poden sol·licitar funcions. El formulari "
"d'enviament de problemes proporciona plantilles per a cadascun per "
"simplificar la creació de problemes i el procés de revisió i implementació; "
"també guia a altres llocs amb informació com ara documentació, discussions, "
"programa HackerOne i Weblate Care."

#: contributing/communication.rst:11
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Weblate keys"
msgid "Weblate GitHub Discussions"
msgstr "Claus del Weblate"

#: contributing/communication.rst:12
msgid ""
"`GitHub Discussions <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/weblate/discussions>`_ is "
"a community place. Ideas, Polls, Q&A, and Show and Tell categories can be "
"selected when posting there. General category fits all posts outside those "
"defined categories. Weblate team members occasionally visit Discussions and "
"can also be mentioned by their GitHub usernames."
msgstr ""
"`GitHub Discussions <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/weblate/discussions>`_ és "
"un lloc comunitari. Les categories Idees, Enquestes, Preguntes i Respostes i "
"Mostra i Digues es poden seleccionar en publicar-hi. La categoria general "
"s'adapta a totes les publicacions fora d'aquestes categories definides. Els "
"membres de l'equip de Weblate de tant en tant visiten discussions i també "
"poden ser esmentats pels seus noms d'usuari de GitHub."

#: contributing/communication.rst:18
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Weblate configuration"
msgid "Weblate on Mastodon"
msgstr "Configuració del Weblate"

#: contributing/communication.rst:19
msgid ""
"If you want to attract a wide community of Weblate users, fans, and "
"developers to your case, you can follow and mention `@weblate@fosstodon.org "
"<https://fosstodon.org/@weblate>`_ on Mastodon. The Weblate team boosts good "
"moods and bright ideas!"
msgstr ""
"Si voleu atraure una àmplia comunitat d'usuaris, fans i desenvolupadors de "
"Weblate al vostre cas, podeu seguir i esmentar `@weblate@fosstodon.org "
"<https://fosstodon.org/@weblate>`_ a Mastodon. L'equip de Weblate potencia "
"el bon humor i les idees brillants!"

#: contributing/debugging.rst:2
msgid "Debugging Weblate"
msgstr ""

#: contributing/debugging.rst:4
msgid ""
"Bugs can behave as application crashes or as various misbehavior. You are "
"welcome to collect info on any such issue and submit it to the `issue "
"tracker <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/weblate/issues>`_."
msgstr ""
"Els errors poden comportar-se com a fallades d'aplicacions o com a mal "
"comportament. Us convidem a recollir informació sobre qualsevol problema "
"d'aquest tipus i enviar-lo al `seguidor de problemes <https://github.com/"
"WeblateOrg/weblate/issues>`_."

#: contributing/debugging.rst:9
msgid "Debug mode"
msgstr "Mode de depuració"

#: contributing/debugging.rst:11
msgid ""
"Turning on debug mode will make the exceptions show in the web browser. This "
"is useful to debug issues in the web interface, but not suitable for a "
"production environment because it has performance consequences and might "
"leak private data."
msgstr ""
"Si activeu el mode de depuració, les excepcions es mostraran al navegador "
"web. Això és útil per depurar problemes a la interfície web, però no és "
"adequat per a un entorn de producció perquè té conseqüències de rendiment i "
"pot filtrar dades privades."

#: contributing/debugging.rst:15
msgid ""
"In a production environment, use :setting:`ADMINS` to receive e-mails "
"containing error reports, or configure error collection using a third-party "
"service."
msgstr ""
"En un entorn de producció, utilitzeu :setting:`ADMINS` per rebre correus "
"electrònics que continguin informes d'errors o configureu la recollida "
"d'errors mitjançant un servei de tercers."

#: contributing/debugging.rst:27
msgid "Weblate logs"
msgstr "Registres del lloc web"

#: contributing/debugging.rst:29
msgid ""
"Weblate can produce detailed logs of what is going on in the background. In "
"the default configuration it uses syslog and that makes the log appear "
"either in :file:`/var/log/messages` or :file:`/var/log/syslog` (depending on "
"your syslog daemon configuration)."
msgstr ""
"Weblate pot produir registres detallats del que està passant en segon pla. A "
"la configuració predeterminada, utilitza syslog i això fa que el registre "
"aparegui a :file:`/var/log/messages` o :file:`/var/log/syslog` (segons la "
"configuració del vostre dimoni de syslog)."

#: contributing/debugging.rst:34
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The Celery process (see :ref:`celery`) usually produces its own logs as "
"well. The example system-wide setups logs to several files under :file:`/var/"
"log/celery/`."
msgstr ""
"El procés d'api (vegeu :ref:`api`) normalment també produeix els seus propis "
"registres. L'exemple de configuració de tot el sistema registra diversos "
"fitxers a :file:`/var/log/celery/`."

#: contributing/debugging.rst:37
msgid ""
"Docker containers log to their output (as per usual in the Docker world), so "
"you can look at the logs using ``docker compose logs``. You can get more "
"detailed logs by changing :envvar:`WEBLATE_LOGLEVEL`."
msgstr ""
"Els contenidors Docker es registren a la seva sortida (com és habitual al "
"món Docker), de manera que podeu consultar els registres mitjançant ``docker "
"compose logs``. Podeu obtenir registres més detallats "
"canviant :envvar:`WEBLATE_LOGLEVEL`."

#: contributing/debugging.rst:43
msgid ""
":ref:`sample-configuration` contains :setting:`django:LOGGING` configuration."
msgstr ""
":ref:`sample-configuration` conté la configuració :setting:`django:LOGGING`."

#: contributing/debugging.rst:48
msgid "Not processing background tasks"
msgstr "No es processen tasques en segon pla"

#: contributing/debugging.rst:50
msgid ""
"A lot of things are done in the background by Celery workers. If things like "
"sending out e-mails or component removal does not work, there might a "
"related issue."
msgstr ""
"Moltes coses les fan en segon pla els treballadors de l'api. Si coses com "
"l'enviament de correus electrònics o l'eliminació de components no "
"funcionen, pot ser que hi hagi un problema relacionat."

#: contributing/debugging.rst:54
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Things to check"
msgid "Things to check in that case:"
msgstr "Elements a comprovar"

#: contributing/debugging.rst:56
#, fuzzy
msgid "Check that the Celery process is running, see :ref:`celery`"
msgstr "Comproveu que el procés d'api s'està executant, vegeu :ref:`api`"

#: contributing/debugging.rst:57
msgid ""
"Check the Celery queue status, either in :ref:`management-interface`, or "
"using :wladmin:`celery_queues`"
msgstr ""
"Comproveu l'estat de la cua d'api, ja sigui a :ref:`management-interface` o "
"utilitzant :wladmin:`celery_queues`"

#: contributing/debugging.rst:58
msgid "Look in the Celery logs for errors (see :ref:`weblate-logs`)"
msgstr "Busqueu errors als registres de Celery (vegeu :ref:`weblate-logs`)"

#: contributing/debugging.rst:63
msgid "Not receiving e-mails from Weblate"
msgstr "No rebre correus electrònics de Weblate"

#: contributing/debugging.rst:65
msgid ""
"You can verify whether outgoing e-mail is working correctly by using "
"the :djadmin:`django:sendtestemail` management command (see :ref:`invoke-"
"manage` for instructions on how to invoke it in different environments) or "
"by using :ref:`management-interface` under the :guilabel:`Tools` tab."
msgstr ""
"Podeu verificar si el correu electrònic de sortida funciona correctament "
"utilitzant l'ordre de gestió :djadmin:`django:sendtestemail` "
"(vegeu :ref:`invoke-manage` per obtenir instruccions sobre com invocar-lo en "
"diferents entorns) o utilitzant :ref:`management-interface` a la "
"pestanya :guilabel:`Tools`."

#: contributing/debugging.rst:70
msgid ""
"These send e-mails directly, so this verifies that your SMTP configuration "
"is correct (see :ref:`out-mail`). Most of the e-mails from Weblate are "
"however sent in the background and there might be some issues with Celery "
"involved as well, please see :ref:`debug-tasks` for debugging that."
msgstr ""
"Aquests envien correus electrònics directament, de manera que això verifica "
"que la vostra configuració SMTP sigui correcta (vegeu :ref:`out-mail`). "
"Tanmateix, la majoria dels correus electrònics de Weblate s'envien en segon "
"pla i també hi pot haver alguns problemes amb Celery, si us plau, "
"vegeu :ref:`debug-tasks` per depurar-ho."

#: contributing/debugging.rst:76
msgid "Analyzing application crashes"
msgstr "Anàlisi de fallades d'aplicacions"

#: contributing/debugging.rst:78
msgid ""
"In case the application crashes, it is useful to collect as much info about "
"the crash as possible. This can be achieved by using third-party services "
"which can collect such info automatically. You can find info on how to set "
"this up in :ref:`collecting-errors`."
msgstr ""
"En cas que l'aplicació es bloquegi, és útil recollir la màxima informació "
"possible sobre el bloqueig. Això es pot aconseguir mitjançant l'ús de "
"serveis de tercers que poden recopilar aquesta informació automàticament. "
"Podeu trobar informació sobre com configurar-ho a :ref:`collecting-errors`."

#: contributing/debugging.rst:84
msgid "Silent failures"
msgstr "Falles silencioses"

#: contributing/debugging.rst:86
msgid ""
"Lots of tasks are offloaded to Celery for background processing. Failures "
"are not shown in the user interface, but appear in the Celery logs. "
"Configuring :ref:`collecting-errors` helps you to notice such failures "
"easier."
msgstr ""
"Es descarreguen moltes tasques a Celery per al processament en segon pla. "
"Els errors no es mostren a la interfície d'usuari, però apareixen als "
"registres de Celery. Configurar :ref:`collecting-errors` us ajuda a detectar "
"aquests errors més fàcilment."

#: contributing/debugging.rst:91
msgid "Performance issues"
msgstr "Problemes de rendiment"

#: contributing/debugging.rst:93
msgid ""
"In case Weblate performs badly in some scenario, please collect the relevant "
"logs showing the issue, and anything that might help figuring out where the "
"code might be improved."
msgstr ""
"En cas que Weblate funcioni malament en algun escenari, si us plau, recull "
"els registres pertinents que mostren el problema i qualsevol cosa que pugui "
"ajudar a esbrinar on es pot millorar el codi."

#: contributing/debugging.rst:97
msgid ""
"See :ref:`collecting-errors` for information on setting up Sentry which can "
"provide useful insights on badly performing operations."
msgstr ""
"Vegeu :ref:`collecting-errors` per obtenir informació sobre com configurar "
"Sentry, que pot proporcionar informació útil sobre les operacions que es fan "
"malament."

#: contributing/debugging.rst:100
msgid ""
"In case the slow performance is linked to the database, you can also enable "
"logging of all database queries using following configuration after "
"enabling :setting:`DEBUG`:"
msgstr ""
"En cas que el rendiment lent estigui vinculat a la base de dades, també "
"podeu habilitar el registre de totes les consultes de la base de dades "
"mitjançant la configuració següent després d'habilitar :setting:`DEBUG`:"

