#: contributing/issues.rst:15
msgid ""
"If you are not sure about your bug report or feature request, you can "
"try :ref:`discussions`."
msgstr ""
"Si no esteu segur del vostre informe d'error o de la vostra sol·licitud de "
"funció, podeu provar :ref:`discussions`."

