"Vegeu :file:`ACCESSIBILITY.md` per a l'objectiu d'accessibilitat de Weblate "
"i la guia d'informes."

#: contributing/issues.rst:39
msgid "Using AI to create issues"
msgstr "Ús de la IA per crear problemes"

#: contributing/issues.rst:41
msgid ""
"If you asked an AI tool to find problems in Weblate or its modules, you "
"**must** make sure to reveal this fact in your report."
msgstr ""
"Si heu demanat a una eina d'IA per trobar problemes a Weblate o als seus "
"mòduls, **hauràs** d'assegurar-vos de revelar aquest fet al vostre informe."

#: contributing/issues.rst:44
msgid ""
"You must also double-check the findings carefully before reporting them to "
"us to validate that the issues are indeed existing and working exactly as "
"the AI says. AI-based tools frequently generate inaccurate or fabricated "
"results."
msgstr ""
"També heu de revisar acuradament les troballes abans d'informar-nos-en per "
"validar que els problemes existeixen i funcionen exactament com diu l'IA. "
"Les eines basades en IA generen sovint resultats inexactes o fabricats."

#: contributing/issues.rst:48
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "It is *rarely* a good idea to just copy and paste an AI-generated report "
#| "to the project. Those generated reports typically are too wordy and "
#| "rarely to the point (in addition to the common fabricated details). If "
#| "you actually discover a issue with an AI and you have verified it "
#| "yourself to be true, write the report yourself and explain the issue as "
#| "you have learned it. This makes sure the AI-generated inaccuracies and "
#| "invented issues are filtered out early before they waste more people's "
#| "time."
msgid ""
"It is *rarely* a good idea to just copy and paste an AI-generated report to "
"the project. Those generated reports typically are too wordy and rarely to "
"the point (in addition to the common fabricated details). If you actually "
"discover an issue with an AI and you have verified it yourself to be true, "
"write the report yourself and explain the issue as you have learned it. This "
"makes sure the AI-generated inaccuracies and invented issues are filtered "
"out early before they waste more people's time."
msgstr ""
"*Poques vegades* és una bona idea copiar i enganxar un informe generat per "
"IA al projecte. Els informes generats solen ser massa pronunciats i poques "
"vegades al punt (a més dels detalls comuns fabricats). Si realment "
"descobreixes un problema amb una IA i has verificat tu mateix que és cert, "
"escriviu l'informe vosaltres mateixos i expliqueu el problema tal com l'heu "
"après. Això assegura que les imprecisions generades per la IA i els "
"problemes inventats es filtren aviat abans que facin perdre el temps de més "
"gent."

#: contributing/issues.rst:56
msgid ""
"As we take security reports seriously, we investigate each report with "
"priority. This work is both time- and energy-consuming and pulls us away "
"from doing other meaningful work. Fake and otherwise made-up security issues "
"effectively prevent us from doing real project work and make us waste time "
"and resources."
msgstr ""
"Com que ens prenem seriosament els informes de seguretat, investiguem cada "
"informe amb prioritat. Aquest treball requereix temps i energia i ens "
"allunya de fer altres treballs significatius. Els problemes de seguretat "
"falsos i inventats d'una altra manera ens impedeixen fer un treball real de "
"projecte i ens fan perdre temps i recursos."

#: contributing/issues.rst:62
msgid ""
"We ban users immediately who submit made-up fake reports to the project."
msgstr ""
"Prohibem immediatament els usuaris que enviïn informes falsos inventats al "
"projecte."

