msgstr ""
"No utilitzeu marques comercials de Weblate en mercaderies a la venda (p. "
"ex., vendre samarretes, tasses, etc.)."

#: contributing/trademark.rst:43
msgid ""
"Don't use Weblate trademarks for any other form of commercial use (e.g. "
"offering technical support services)."
msgstr ""
"No utilitzeu les marques comercials de Weblate per a cap altra forma d'ús "
"comercial (per exemple, oferir serveis d'assistència tècnica)."

#: contributing/trademark.rst:44
msgid ""
"Don't modify Weblate's trademarks, abbreviate them, or combine them with any "
