#: devel/community.rst:13
msgid ""
"Guidance is shown in the :guilabel:`Diagnostics` tab on each component. "
"These alerts are dismissible and point to the configuration or documentation "
"needed to make your localization process easier for community translators."
msgstr ""
"Les instruccions es mostren a la pestanya :guilabel:`Diagnòstics` de cada "
"component. Aquestes alertes es poden descartar i apunten a la configuració o "
