#: faq.rst:2
msgid "Frequently Asked Questions"
msgstr "Preguntes freqüents"

#: faq.rst:10
msgid "How to create an automated workflow?"
msgstr "Com crear un flux de treball automatitzat?"

#: faq.rst:12
msgid ""
"Weblate can handle all the translation things semi-automatically for you. If "
"you give it push access to your repository, the translations can happen "
"without interaction, unless some merge conflict occurs."
msgstr ""
"Weblate pot gestionar totes les coses de traducció de manera semiautomàtica "
"per a vostè. Si li doneu accés push al vostre dipòsit, les traduccions es "
"poden produir sense interacció, tret que es produeixi algun conflicte de "
"combinació."

#: faq.rst:16
msgid ""
"Set up your Git repository to tell Weblate when there is any change, "
"see :ref:`hooks` for info on how to do it."
msgstr ""
"Configureu el vostre repositori Git per dir-li a Weblate quan hi ha cap "
"canvi, vegeu :ref:`hooks` per obtenir informació sobre com fer-ho."

#: faq.rst:18
msgid ""
"Set a push URL at your :ref:`component` in Weblate, this allows Weblate to "
"push changes to your repository."
msgstr ""
"Establiu un URL push al vostre :ref:`component` a Weblate, això permet que "
"Weblate publiqui canvis al vostre repositori."

#: faq.rst:20
msgid ""
"Turn on :ref:`component-push_on_commit` on your :ref:`component` in Weblate, "
"this will make Weblate push changes to your repository whenever they happen "
