"as terminology` adds entries for them to all languages in the glossary. Use "
"this for important terms that should be well thought out, and retain a "
"consistent meaning across all languages."
msgstr ""
"Marcar certs termes del glossari com a ``terminologia`` mitjançant l'edició "
"massiva, escrivint el senyalador o utilitzant :guilabel:`Eines` "
"↓ :guilabel:`Marca com a terminologia` afegeix entrades per a ells a tots "
"els idiomes del glossari. Utilitzeu-ho per a termes importants que haurien "
"d'estar ben pensats i mantenir un significat coherent en totes les llengües."

#: user/glossary.rst:177
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "While the flag remains on the term, Weblate treats it as terminology and "
#| "keeps an entry for it in every glossary language. If a language entry is "
#| "removed, the next glossary synchronization creates it again."
msgid ""
"The terminology flag is ongoing state, not just a one-time action. While the "
"flag remains on the source term, Weblate treats it as terminology and keeps "
"an entry for it in every glossary language. If a language entry is removed, "
"the next glossary synchronization creates it again."
msgstr ""
"Tot i que la bandera es manté al terme, Weblate la tracta com a terminologia "
"i en conserva una entrada en tots els idiomes del glossari. Si s'elimina una "
"entrada d'idioma, la següent sincronització del glossari la crea de nou."

#: user/glossary.rst:182
msgid ""
"Removing the ``terminology`` flag stops this automatic maintenance, but it "
"does not remove or otherwise revert entries that were already created. They "
"remain regular glossary entries."
msgstr ""
"L'eliminació de la marca ``terminologia`` atura aquest manteniment "
"automàtic, però no elimina ni reverteix les entrades que ja es van crear. "
"Continuen sent entrades habituals de glossari."

#: user/glossary.rst:186
msgid ""
"A regular glossary term can also have translations in every language. The "
"difference is that Weblate does not recreate missing language entries for a "
"regular term after they are removed."
msgstr ""

#: user/glossary.rst:197 user/translating.rst:107
