"translations, and one able to review them to ensure translations are "
"consistent and that the quality is good."
msgstr ""
"Amb revisors dedicats, teniu dos grups d'usuaris, un pot enviar traduccions "
"i un altre capaç de revisar-les per garantir que les traduccions siguin "
"coherents i que la qualitat sigui bona."

#: workflows.rst:178
msgid "*Any user* can edit unapproved translations."
msgstr "*Qualsevol usuari* pot editar les traduccions no aprovades."

#: workflows.rst:179
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Requires dedicated reviewers to approve source strings."
msgid "*Reviewer* can approve / unapprove strings."
msgstr "Calen revisors dedicats que aprovin les cadenes d’origen."

#: workflows.rst:180
msgid "*Reviewer* can edit all translations (including approved ones)."
msgstr ""
"*El revisor* pot editar totes les traduccions (incloses les aprovades)."

#: workflows.rst:181
msgid "Suggestions can also be used to suggest changes for approved strings."
msgstr ""
"Els suggeriments també es poden utilitzar per suggerir canvis per a les "
"cadenes aprovades."

#: workflows.rst:199
#, fuzzy
msgid "Or `Review` with :ref:`per-project access control <manage-acl>`."
msgstr "O `Revisió' amb :ref:`control d'accés per projecte <manage-acl>`."

#: workflows.rst:205
msgid "Turning on reviews"
msgstr "S'està activant les ressenyes"

#: workflows.rst:207
msgid ""
"Reviews can be turned on in the project configuration, from "
"the :guilabel:`Workflow` subpage of project settings (to be found in "
"the :guilabel:`Operations` → :guilabel:`Settings` menu):"
msgstr ""
"Les revisions es poden activar a la configuració del projecte, des de la "
"subpàgina :guilabel:`Flux de treball` de la configuració del projecte (que "
"es pot trobar al menú :guilabel:`Operacions` → :guilabel:`Configuració`):"

#: workflows.rst:214
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Per language"
msgid "Per-language reviews"
msgstr "Per llengua"

#: workflows.rst:216
msgid ""
"To require review only for selected languages, first turn on :ref:`project-"
"translation_review` for the whole project. Then open each project language "
"page that should use different behavior, enable :guilabel:`Customize "
"translation workflow for this language in this project`, and "
"turn :guilabel:`Enable reviews` off for languages that should not require "
"review."
msgstr ""

#: workflows.rst:223
msgid ""
"Reviewers also need review access for the same language. Add them to a team "
"whose roles include :guilabel:`Review strings`, and limit that team or the "
"user membership to the language they should review. See :ref:`manage-acl` "
"and :ref:`custom-acl` for language-scoped access setup."
msgstr ""

#: workflows.rst:228
msgid ""
"If approval buttons are not visible, check both parts of the setup: reviews "
"have to be enabled for that translation, and the signed-in user has to have "
"review permission for that language."
msgstr ""

#: workflows.rst:235
msgid "Quality gateway for the source strings"
msgstr "Passarel·la de qualitat per a les cadenes d'origen"

#: workflows.rst:237
msgid ""
"The original source language strings usually come from developers, since "
"they write the code and provide the initial strings. However, developers are "
"often not native speakers of the source language and do not provide the "
"desired quality of the source strings. The intermediate translation can help "
"you address this - there is an additional quality gateway for the strings "
"between developers and translators."
msgstr ""
"Les cadenes de l'idioma font original solen venir dels desenvolupadors, ja "
"que escriuen el codi i proporcionen les cadenes inicials. Tanmateix, sovint "
"els desenvolupadors no són parlants nadius de l'idioma font i no "
"proporcionen la qualitat desitjada de les cadenes d'origen. La traducció "
"intermèdia us pot ajudar a solucionar-ho: hi ha una passarel·la de qualitat "
"addicional per a les cadenes entre desenvolupadors i traductors."

#: workflows.rst:244
msgid ""
"By setting the :ref:`component-intermediate`, this file is used for "
"translating strings to the source language by translators/editors while it "
"is owned by the developers (often using arbitrary languages such as "
"``en_devel``). Once this stage is done, strings are available for "
"translations to target languages, based on what is now a polished source "
"language stored in the :ref:`component-template`."
msgstr ""
"En establir el :ref:`component-intermediate`, aquest fitxer s'utilitza per "
"traduir cadenes a l'idioma font pels traductors/editors mentre és propietat "
"dels desenvolupadors (sovint utilitzant llenguatges arbitraris com "
"``en_devel``). Un cop finalitzada aquesta etapa, les cadenes estan "
"disponibles per a les traduccions als idiomes de destinació, basant-se en el "
"que ara és un idioma font polit emmagatzemat a la :ref:`component-template`."

#: workflows.rst:297
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Start new translation into more languages"
msgid "String consolidation using secondary language"
msgstr "Inicia una traducció nova en més llengües"

#: workflows.rst:299
msgid ""
"When :ref:`component-intermediate` cannot be used to consolidate the "
"strings, you can choose one of the translations to act as a secondary "
"language. The language can be configured in a project (:ref:`project-"
"secondary_language`) or in a component (:ref:`component-"
"secondary_language`). It is then shown to the translators while translating "
"(see :ref:`secondary-languages`) and can be optionally used as a source for "
"machine translations (see :ref:`mt-sources`)."
msgstr ""
"Quan :ref:`component-intermediate` no es pot utilitzar per consolidar les "
"cadenes, podeu triar una de les traduccions perquè actuï com a idioma "
"secundari. L'idioma es pot configurar en un projecte (:ref:`project-"
"secondary_language`) o en un component (:ref:`component-"
"secondary_language`). A continuació, es mostra als traductors mentre "
"tradueixen (vegeu :ref:`secondary-languages`) i es pot utilitzar "
"opcionalment com a font per a traduccions automàtices (vegeu :ref:`mt-"
"sources`)."

#: workflows.rst:307
msgid ""
"This setup can be useful with mixed language source strings and "
"consolidating them into a single translation, which is then used as a "
"baseline for other work."
msgstr ""
"Aquesta configuració pot ser útil amb cadenes d'origen mixtes i consolidar-"
"les en una única traducció, que després s'utilitza com a línia de base per a "
"altres treballs."

#: workflows.rst:313
msgid "Source strings reviews"
msgstr "Ressenyes de cadenes d'origen"

#: workflows.rst:315
msgid ""
"With :ref:`project-source_review` enabled, the review process can be applied "
"for source strings. Once enabled, users can report issues with source "
"strings. The actual process depends on whether bilingual or monolingual "
"formats are in use."
msgstr ""
"Amb :ref:`project-source_review` activat, el procés de revisió es pot "
"aplicar a les cadenes d'origen. Un cop habilitat, els usuaris poden informar "
"de problemes amb les cadenes d'origen. El procés real depèn de si "
"s'utilitzen formats bilingües o monolingües."

#: workflows.rst:319
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"For monolingual formats, source string review functions similarly "
"to :ref:`reviews` — once an issue with a source string is reported, the "
"source string is marked as :guilabel:`Needs editing`."
msgstr ""
"Per als formats monolingües, la revisió de la cadena d'origen funciona de "
"manera semblant a :ref:`revisions' — un cop s'informa d'un problema amb una "
"cadena d'origen, la cadena d'origen es marca com a :guilabel:`Necessita "
"edició`."

#: workflows.rst:323
msgid ""
"Bilingual formats do not allow direct editing of source strings (these are "
"typically extracted directly from the source code). In this case, "
"a :guilabel:`Source needs review` label is attached to strings reported by "
"translators. You should review such strings and either edit them in the "
"source code, or remove the label."
msgstr ""
"Els formats bilingües no permeten l'edició directa de les cadenes font "
"(normalment s'extreuen directament del codi font). En aquest cas, s'adjunta "
"una etiqueta :guilabel:`La font necessita una revisió` a les cadenes "
"informades pels traductors. Hauríeu de revisar aquestes cadenes i editar-les "
"al codi font o eliminar l'etiqueta."

